#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:78
msgid "### Restoration methods"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:80
msgid ""
"Depending on the utilities available, it will be possible to perform several "
"types of restorations."
