#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:479
msgid ""
"``` $ tar xvfz backup.tar.gz /path/to/file $ tar xvfj backup.tar.bz2 /path/"
"to/file ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:481
msgid "##### Extract a folder from a backup _tar_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:483
msgid ""
"To extract only one directory (including its subdirectories and files) from "
"a backup, specify the directory name at the end of the `tar xvf` command."
