#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/09-backups.md:495
msgid ""
"``` $ tar xvf backup.tar /path/to/dir1/ /path/to/dir2/ $ tar xvfz backup.tar."
"gz /path/to/dir1/ /path/to/dir2/ $ tar xvfj backup.tar.bz2 /path/to/dir1/ /"
"path/to/dir2/ ```"
